<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//op-talk.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/01/14/dont-be-afraid-of-robots-says-ayanna-howard/" data-title="Donât Be Afraid of Robots, Says Ayanna Howard" data-description="Some say robots will replace us at work. But Dr. Howard, a professor of electrical and computer engineering, thinks they could actually help Americans get jobs.">
